{{version030}}

{{flavour|Conjures a focused blast of highly toxic sludge, poisoning the victim and drenching their surroundings. The sludge damages and poisons all monsters, even those resistant to poison.}}

'''Hurl Sludge''' is a monster-only spell that deals damage. It creates a short-lived tile of [[Eringya's Noxious Bog|toxic sludge]] where it lands, which deals heavy poison damage to non-[[flying]] creatures (and otherwise acts like [[shallow water]]). Sludge lasts for 2-3 turns. It can replace staircases and certain other dungeon features.

{{monsters with spell}}

==History==
*This spell was added in [[0.26]].

